<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Your Course!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .greeting-text {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .course-title {
            background-color: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .start-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .start-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            background-color: #2563eb;
        }
        .features-list {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .features-list h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #3b82f6;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .support-link {
            color: #3b82f6;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .support-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üéâ Welcome to Your New Course!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting-text">Hi {{firstName}},</p>
            
            <p>Congratulations! You've successfully enrolled in:</p>
            
            <div class="course-title">
                üìö {{courseTitle}}
            </div>
            
            <p>You're all set to start your learning journey! Here's what you can do next:</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{courseUrl}}" class="start-button">
                    üöÄ Start Learning Now
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="features-list">
                <h3>‚ú® What's included in your course:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>üìñ Comprehensive course materials</li>
                    <li>üé• Video lessons and tutorials</li>
                    <li>üìù Interactive quizzes and assessments</li>
                    <li>üìä Progress tracking</li>
                    <li>üèÜ Certificate upon completion</li>
                    <li>üí¨ Access to course community</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>Pro Tips:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Set aside dedicated time each day for learning</li>
                <li>Take notes and complete all assignments</li>
                <li>Engage with other learners in the community</li>
                <li>Don't hesitate to ask questions if you need help</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>Ready to begin? Click the button above to access your course dashboard and start learning!</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" class="support-link">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 E-Learning Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 